          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Birmingham Services CTA -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-[#FFA985]/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Professional Medical Office Cleaning in Birmingham</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">The Valley Clean Team serves healthcare practices throughout Jefferson County with HIPAA-aware, clinical-grade cleaning.</p>
